ke `user..name@example.com` with MailAddress, and uses Uri for 10K+ character URLs.\nWhat breaks?","attachments":[],"interactionId":"9cc90ad4-6b10-41ac-a835-2f34b2c74133"},"id":"5e33f5c8-76c5-43b6-9914-5f79133bc90f","timestamp":"2026-05-10T01:11:15.110Z","parentId":"b49e1b9c-a27e-4f13-accb-ebfca7482130"}
